<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Login Gagal</title>

<style>
*{
  margin:0;
  padding:0;
  box-sizing:border-box;
  font-family:'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
}

body{
  height:100vh;
  display:flex;
  justify-content:center;
  align-items:center;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,#141e30,#243b55);
  color:#fff;
}

.container{
  text-align:center;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  padding:55px 45px;
  border-radius:22px;
  backdrop-filter:blur(14px);
  box-shadow:0 18px 45px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
  max-width:520px;
  width:92%;
  animation:fadeIn 0.7s ease;
}

.icon{
  font-size:85px;
  margin-bottom:18px;
  animation:shake 0.6s ease;
}

h1{
  font-size:34px;
  margin-bottom:12px;
  letter-spacing:1px;
}

p{
  font-size:16px;
  opacity:0.92;
  margin-bottom:28px;
  line-height:1.7;
}

.actions{
  display:flex;
  gap:14px;
  justify-content:center;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
}

.btn{
  padding:13px 26px;
  border-radius:30px;
  text-decoration:none;
  font-weight:bold;
  transition:0.3s;
}

.btn-primary{
  background:#ff5f6d;
  color:white;
  box-shadow:0 10px 25px rgba(255,95,109,0.45);
}

.btn-primary:hover{
  transform:translateY(-3px);
  box-shadow:0 14px 30px rgba(255,95,109,0.6);
}

.btn-secondary{
  background:transparent;
  border:2px solid #fff;
  color:#fff;
}

.btn-secondary:hover{
  background:#fff;
  color:#243b55;
}

.note{
  margin-top:22px;
  font-size:13px;
  opacity:0.75;
}

@keyframes fadeIn{
  from{opacity:0; transform:translateY(18px);}
  to{opacity:1; transform:translateY(0);}
}

@keyframes shake{
  0%{transform:translateX(0);}
  25%{transform:translateX(-9px);}
  50%{transform:translateX(9px);}
  75%{transform:translateX(-6px);}
  100%{transform:translateX(0);}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">
  <div class="icon">🚫</div>
  <h1>Login Gagal</h1>
  <p>
    Username atau password yang kamu masukkan salah.<br>
    Periksa kembali data login kamu dan coba lagi.
  </p>

  <div class="actions">
    <a href="/#login" class="btn btn-primary">Coba Login Lagi</a>
    <a href="/#register" class="btn btn-secondary">Belum Punya Akun?</a>
  </div>

  <div class="note">
    Demi keamanan, sistem tidak memberi tahu bagian mana yang salah.
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
